				<td colspan="2"><span>I'm having a hard time calculating how much damage I can do with various items and gear using the <a href="http://www.eqdiva.com/Forums/ShowPost.aspx?PostID=53593">BardSong spreadsheet</a>.
<br />

<br />
When I use CoPlague(61) with my Thunderous Drum of Karana as the only percussion modifier, I do 114 damage per tick. When I look at the spreadsheet, I see 114 under &quot;Instrument&quot;.
<br />

<br />
When I add in the Singing Short Sword, the &quot;Instrument&quot; number does not go up, only the Item number. I thought that it would stack...?
<br />

<br />
So I'm kind of confused about how stacking works. If I have the Painted Primal Mask (1.4 singing) and the Larva Skin Cape (1.6 singing) will I do more damage with Mischeif (62)? What if I have those 2 items and also equip my Orcish Lute of Singing (2.1)?
<br />

<br />
Since I don't have my epic, I rely on my gear quite a bit. Just need to know if I should be equipping an instrument as well.</span></td>
