			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>You are correct that an augment's modifier will not stack with another pre-existing mod.  However, there is a situation in which putting it into a piece of gear with a mod is NOT a waste -- and that is if we're talking about 2 different mods.  So let's say you buy the LDON lute, Rujarkian Lute of Battle, and augment it with the brass augment from Guk, the Limestone Shard of Battle Cries.  Now you have a lute that has a 2.6 string mod and a 1.8 brass mod in one slot.</span></td>
